description:
This is a 20 minute workout called '70s HIIT Elliptical Workout | Elliptical Machine Class to 70s Pop | Fitscope Studio' from the channel Fitscope.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Nightclub Workout and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: 70s HIIT Elliptical Workout | Elliptical Machine Class to 70s Pop | Fitscope Studio

Join Meghan for this short but intense elliptical machine interval workout. Meghan makes use of both resistance and inclines intervals with a happy 70s pop soundtrack including Sister Sledge, Abba, Elton John, Diana Ross and more. 

Class Plan: 
5 min warmup
4 min intervals
1 min cool down
